==========================================
Description of the files in this directory
==========================================

LAYER 0 : 
SnpsRisc8_Common_Bool.ova : This file contains definition of common boolean.
			
LAYER 1:
SnpsRisc8_WhiteBox_Rules.ova : This file contains definition for event and 
                               assert based on the internal level 
                               specification.  

LAYER 2:
SnpsRisc8_WhiteBox_Unit.ova : This file contains OVA unit definition of DUT. 
SnpsRisc8_WhiteBox_Bind.ova : This file binds the OVA unit to DUT.
LAYER 3:
SnpsRisc8.ovah : Configuration file for different option to control ova.
